# Deploy Apps to Amplify / ECS

Use when the user asks to **deploy** one or more apps under `F:\project_workspace\`, **merge local work into release/deploy branches**, and **push** so production CI runs.

**Prerequisite rules (commit + secret filter first):**
- [git_commit_push_release_deploy.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/git_commit_push_release_deploy.mdc) — commit, push work branch, release merge
- [git_local_push.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/git_local_push.mdc) — `GIT_SSL_NO_VERIFY`, secret scan, pull-before-push

